---
title: Simple Lamb Ragù with Roasted Sweet Pepper and Spinach
description: At HelloFresh we're excited to bring variety to your dinner table! It's easy to always reach for ground beef when making a pasta sauce. Why not try delicious lamb? Paired with sweet roasted peppers and a rich ragù sauce, no one would believe you made this at home!
